title: [Imaera's Poem, Basingstroke]
[Imaera's Poem, Basingstoke]
description: Thick vines and brilliantly colored flowers cover the walls of the small room.  Peacock feathers have been strung from the ceiling alongside tiny carvings of birds in flight.  A low wooden table sits to one side of the room with a small sign that reads "Women."  To the other side of the room is a set of shell-carved wooden shelves with a sign that reads "Men."
